%% Diagram: Request coalescing (single-flight) collapses concurrent misses to one DB query
%% Type: sequence
sequenceDiagram
    participant C1 as Caller 1
    participant C2 as Caller 2..N
    participant SF as Singleflight group
    participant Cache
    participant DB

    C1->>Cache: GET key
    Cache-->>C1: miss
    C1->>SF: Do(key, fetch)
    Note over SF: Caller 1 becomes the leader, key marked in-flight

    C2->>Cache: GET key
    Cache-->>C2: miss
    C2->>SF: Do(key, fetch)
    Note over SF: Callers 2..N attach to the leader, no extra DB call

    SF->>DB: SELECT key
    DB-->>SF: value
    SF->>Cache: SET key value
    SF-->>C1: value
    SF-->>C2: value
    Note over SF: 10K concurrent missers collapse to 1 DB query
